    parentName: "p"
  }, "inoculation"), ", because it prevents objections before they happen."), mdx("p", null, "For instance, after you explain the amazing upsides of your tax software, briefly point out which of these features and benefits aren't available from anyone else. Once it's clear that competitors can't offer the same value as your excellent cost-cutting tools, your buyer won't consider anyone else."), mdx("ol", {
